title: The Punisher
description: After his wife and child murdered Frank Castle (Thomas Jane) decided to dedicate his life to eliminate crime from the streets of the city in which he lives. For both Castle not only pursues the bandits but also eliminates using for both his experience as FBI undercover agent. His new target is Howard Saint (John Travolta), a man connected to the criminal underworld who decides to take revenge from society after her dead son.
